root.content:
&lt;p&gt;
	&lt;span&nbsp;style=\"color:\"&nbsp;rgb(17,=\"\"&nbsp;17,=\"\"&nbsp;17);=\"\"&nbsp;font-family:=\"\"&nbsp;宋体,=\"\"&nbsp;微软雅黑,=\"\"&nbsp;verdana,=\"\"&nbsp;helvetica;=\"\"&nbsp;line-height:=\"\"&nbsp;25px;=\"\"&gt;Jquery的自适应宽度圆角按钮，给你提供一个思路，按钮的长度随你的文字多少自动伸长，用着更省心。而且鼠标放在按钮上，按钮还会变颜色呢，漂亮吧。兼容性貌似也不错，感谢作者的分享。原理很简单，就是在input的前后各追加一个DIV来实现圆角&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
	&lt;span&nbsp;style=\"color:\"&nbsp;rgb(17,=\"\"&nbsp;17,=\"\"&nbsp;17);=\"\"&nbsp;font-family:=\"\"&nbsp;宋体,=\"\"&nbsp;微软雅黑,=\"\"&nbsp;verdana,=\"\"&nbsp;helvetica;=\"\"&nbsp;line-height:=\"\"&nbsp;25px;=\"\"&gt;
&lt;pre&nbsp;name=\"code\"&nbsp;id=\"prettyprint\"&nbsp;class=\"html\"&gt;&amp;lt;!DOCTYPE&nbsp;html&nbsp;PUBLIC&nbsp;-//W3C//DTD&nbsp;XHTML&nbsp;1.0&nbsp;Transitional//EN&nbsp;http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd&amp;gt;
&amp;lt;html&nbsp;xmlns=http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&amp;gt;
&amp;lt;head&amp;gt;
&amp;lt;meta&nbsp;http-equiv=Content-Type&nbsp;content=text/html;&nbsp;charset=gb2312&nbsp;/&amp;gt;
&amp;lt;title&amp;gt;基于Jquery的自适应宽度圆角按钮&amp;lt;/title&amp;gt;
&amp;lt;script&nbsp;language=JavaScript&nbsp;type=text/javascript&nbsp;src=http://code.jquery.com/jquery-1.4.2.min.js&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/script&amp;gt;
&amp;lt;style&nbsp;type=text/css&amp;gt;
.left&nbsp;{background:url(http://www.poluoluo.com/jzxy/UploadFiles_333/201108/20110806152705293.jpg)&nbsp;left&nbsp;no-repeat;&nbsp;height:26px;&nbsp;margin:0&nbsp;4px;&nbsp;padding:0&nbsp;0&nbsp;0&nbsp;6px;&nbsp;*padding:0;&nbsp;font-size:12px;}
.leftHover&nbsp;{background:url(http://www.poluoluo.com/jzxy/UploadFiles_333/201108/20110806152706285.jpg)&nbsp;left&nbsp;no-repeat;}
.right&nbsp;{background:url(http://www.poluoluo.com/jzxy/UploadFiles_333/201108/20110806152706428.jpg)&nbsp;right&nbsp;no-repeat;&nbsp;height:26px;&nbsp;width:6px;&nbsp;float:left;}
.rightHover&nbsp;{&nbsp;background:url(http://www.poluoluo.com/jzxy/UploadFiles_333/201108/20110806152707177.jpg)&nbsp;right&nbsp;no-repeat;}
.bot&nbsp;{float:left;border:none;&nbsp;border:0;&nbsp;line-height:26px;&nbsp;color:#fff;&nbsp;font-family:微软雅黑;&nbsp;cursor:pointer;&nbsp;height:26px;&nbsp;background:url(http://www.poluoluo.com/jzxy/UploadFiles_333/201108/20110806152707742.jpg)&nbsp;repeat-x;}
.botHover&nbsp;{background:url(http://www.poluoluo.com/jzxy/UploadFiles_333/201108/20110806152707187.jpg)&nbsp;repeat-x;}

&amp;lt;/style&amp;gt;
&amp;lt;script&nbsp;type=text/javascript&amp;gt;
$(document).ready(function(){
$(:input[type=&nbsp;button&nbsp;]).wrap(&amp;lt;div&nbsp;class=&nbsp;left&nbsp;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/div&amp;gt;).after(&amp;lt;div&nbsp;class=&nbsp;right&nbsp;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/div&amp;gt;).addClass(bot);
$(&nbsp;.left&nbsp;).hover(function(){
$(this).addClass(leftHover);
$(this).find(&nbsp;.bot&nbsp;).addClass(botHover);
$(this).find(&nbsp;.right&nbsp;).addClass(rightHover);
},
function(){$(this).removeClass(leftHover);
$(this).find(&nbsp;.right&nbsp;).removeClass(rightHover);
$(this).find(&nbsp;.bot&nbsp;).removeClass(botHover);});&nbsp;
}
);
&amp;lt;/script&amp;gt;
&amp;lt;/head&amp;gt;
&amp;lt;body&amp;gt;
&amp;lt;input&nbsp;name=&nbsp;type=button&nbsp;value=我很短，但可以适合长的&nbsp;/&amp;gt;&amp;lt;input&nbsp;name=&nbsp;type=button&nbsp;value=我要很长，很长再长，我喜欢长的&nbsp;/&amp;gt;
&amp;lt;input&nbsp;name=&nbsp;type=button&nbsp;value=这个太短了&nbsp;/&amp;gt;
&amp;lt;/body&amp;gt;
